{
  "page": "Mêlée at Runestone",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/21/Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png/350px-Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"379\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/21/Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png/525px-Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/21/Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png/700px-Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Harry_the_Heir_by_Chillyravenart.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a>, by Chillyravenart ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>mêlée at Runestone</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> held at <a href=\"/index.php/Runestone\" title=\"Runestone\">Runestone</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Participants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Participants</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Yohn_Royce\" title=\"Yohn Royce\">Yohn Royce</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Runestone\" title=\"Lord of Runestone\">Lord of Runestone</a>, hosts a small mêlée with squires being the only participants. Bronze Yohn intends for <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Ward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ward\">ward</a> of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a> and the heir of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert Arryn</a>, to be the victor. After Harry the Heir wins the competition, he receives <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighthood</a> from Lord Royce.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Ser Harrold upsets <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a> when they meet at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>. When Alayne encounters Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a>, Lothor refers to Harry as \"some upjumped squire\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Participants\">Participants</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Participants\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hardyng\" title=\"House Hardyng\"><img alt=\"House Hardyng.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/32px-House_Hardyng.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/48px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/House_Hardyng.svg/64px-House_Hardyng.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Myranda</b>: Our cousin <a href=\"/index.php/Yohn_Royce\" title=\"Yohn Royce\">Bronze Yohn</a> had himself a mêlée at <a href=\"/index.php/Runestone\" title=\"Runestone\">Runestone</a>, a small one, just for <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squires</a>. It was meant for Harry the Heir to win the honors, and so he did.<br />\n</p><p><b>Alayne</b>: Harry the Heir?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Myranda</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Lady Waynwood's</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Ward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ward\">ward</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a>. I suppose we must call him Ser Harry now. Bronze Yohn <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighted</a> him.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Myranda_Royce\" title=\"Myranda Royce\">Myranda Royce</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=M%C3%AAl%C3%A9e_at_Runestone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 41\">Chapter 41</a>, Alayne II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Alayne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Alayne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215533\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.061 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 286/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9049/1000000\nPost‐expand include siz